        "id": 1082465
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-08-05T14:54:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "What prompted it initially was, I was trying to issue a new EGL extension string \"EGL_ANDROID_native_fence_sync\" but that didn\u0027t take into account guests that didn\u0027t have the support, and then I ended up leaving the std::string logic in, in order to future proof for any further attempts to change the host EGL string. Plus, we switched to std::string logic for rcGetGLString recently (for actual need to put extra extension strings there). In any case, the declaration and initialization is in one place now.",
      "parentUuid": "54231e3a_3bfb917c",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 187,
        "startChar": 4,
        "endLine": 187,
        "endChar": 17
